name: Space Debris
description: A Local Co-op Zen Space Rock Demolition game. Up to 16 players can play locally on a single screen, collecting space materials to unlock unique ships and upgrades, as well as new features. Drop in/out multiplayer for everyone!

name: Project Shore
description: Project Shore (working title) is a single player tactical RPG in a low fantasy medieval setting, currently in development using Unreal Engine 4 for Windows PC platforms. You play as a newly-made leader of a mercenary company after an assignment gone wrong. Having barely escaped from a deadly encounter with a friend-turned-backstabber, and then another one with an unknown otherwordly force, you need to lead what is left of your squad through the times of tumult while searching for hidden truth of what had really transpired to you.

name: Destination Dungeons: Catacombs of Dreams
description: Destination Dungeon is a new casual style of dungeon crawling. Instead of roaming around a huge dungeon looking for opportunity, the opportunities come to you. Random events take place including traps, locked doors, enemy encounters, merchants, and more.

name: Flotus
description: Show your aptitude, dexterity, knowledge of physics and geometry! Throw the ball into the box with one throw in a new physical puzzle with simple rules and game mechanics in the style of "Angry Birds"!

name: Machine With a Big Gun
description:
Machine With a Big Gun - these are long freeways and hundreds of explosions. You have a difficult road ahead, in which your car and a huge cannon will help you, which shoots long bursts and missiles. 
The world has changed, it is ruled by people, greedy for power, who believe only in brute force. In their way, it's only you! Get to the leaders of local groups and overcome them in a hard fight.

name: Spring of Decadence
description:
The player can manipulate the heroine, and the player can train the character to decide the fate of the character. 
There are hundreds of events and dozens of CG can be collected. 
This game has a very unique story and a world with high degree of freedom.

name: Killer Backflip 999
description: Test yourself for dexterity: dodge strikes, overcome many obstacles! Lasers, blasters, grenades, flamethrowers and much more - everything will go to play.

name: Fairyland: Power Dice
description: Get the power crystals, change the course of the war in your favor, and let the dice decide Fairyland’s fate!

name: Running With Dinosaurs
description:
You must Escape from the hunt for the Dinosaurs and Avoid obstacles, Or you die. 
Control role with WASD.

name: Galdur
description: Galdur is a top-down dungeon crawler with a spell-crafting mechanic as its main feature. Unlock new abilities and ingredients to craft spells and hone your build to defeat hordes of monsters in sprawling, procedurally generated dungeons and to defeat challenging boss fights.

name: Sig
description: SIG - a fascinating puzzle, whose goal is to free space, to connect shapes.

name: Dark Visit
description: Dark Visit; a both psychological and a horror game. You start the game as an old psychologist. You are going to get a suspicious note that will lead you to dark visit.

name: Zombie Barricades
description: Zombie Barricades is a 3rd person, multiplayer RPG featuring customizable weapons, vehicles and physics! Work alone or as a team and mission through the wastelands and construct Barricades to protect yourself from the horde!

name: Jumpo Joe
description: Do you want to boost metabolism, burn some energy and check your endurance? Jumpo Joe is a puzzle-platformer that will help you to do this...

name: Viking Age: Odin's warrior
description: Betrayed by your allies. You must seek revenge and regain your families honour, so they can feast with the gods in the great hall. Experience this massive open world environment rife with danger and suspense. Build your own town, farm, boatyard or explore the lands as a homeless wanderer, the choice is completely yours. Try out the never before seen NPC system that allows you to hire them to do the more grinding tasks. But be careful as once they die they are gone forever. The lands themselves are harsh with a map size of 100km x 100km teaming with a variety of animals to hunt or be hunted by. Travel by your own 2 feet , or if you have the gold you can buy a horse or longboat.

name: Lovecraft Tales
description: Atmospheric, dark adventure set in Lovecraft's universe.

name: Football Story
description: Football Story is a multiplayer football game that pits full teams of players against one another. Each player controls their own character, instead of a full team. In Football Story, you step into the cleats of a player in a small neighborhood club.

name: Mad Manuel
description: Difficult, graphical, fun. A platformer that will make you cry, laugh, and cry again! That's how difficult it is!

name: Canyon Ridge
description:
Canyon Ridge is an autobiographical gaming experience about psychosis, plastic cups, and low resolution reality. 
 
Waking up suddenly in a place with all new faces and names, you must control the Avatar through the trials and minor tribulations befalling him on his quest to debate the seriousness of his mental health.

name: Project 1v1
description: Project 1v1 is the code name for Gearbox's top-secret, in-development, competitive first-person shooter that combines the action of fast-paced 1v1 first-person combat with the metagame strategy of a collectible card game.

name: Elysium VR
description: Elysium is a multiplayer Roleplaying game designed for virtual reality. The player falls into a sandbox world (Saint-Graice islands), in which he or she will live, work and have fun. The everyday life is detailed, starting from the need for water and food, finishing with decoration of their apartment / house. You just have to comfortably settle in this world and go in search of adventure with your friends. Each player can have different jobs, ranging from a dangerous bandit from the hood, ending with the president of the island state of Saint-Graice islands. You are guaranteed to experience maximum immersion in the gameplay! After all, all this will happen in VR ( and PC )!

name: Telltale's Stranger Things Game
description: An unreleased game by Telltale Games based on the Netflix series Stranger Things.

name: Hyper Sports R
description:
"Hyper Sports R, is a new sports simulation title, to arrive on the Nintendo Switch. Compete in a variety of individual and team sports, and train a team to take on rivals as you race for a spot at the top.

In Hyper Sports R, players can choose from a variety of 20+ characters to build up and compete. Become the best competitor in a variety of different sports, which include track and field, beach volleyball and swimming."

name: Morning Star
description: Morning Star is a first-person, post-cyberpunk farming game where computers are your soil and software are your seeds.

name: Fallout 76: Power Armor Edition
description:
Reclamation Day, 2102. Twenty-five years after the bombs fall, you and your fellow Vault Dwellers—chosen from the nation’s best and brightest – emerge into post-nuclear America. Play solo or join together as you explore, quest, build, and triumph against the wasteland’s greatest threats.

In addition to the highly-anticipated game, the Fallout 76 Power Armor Edition includes:

* Full-Scale Wearable T-51 Power Armor Helmet with West Tek Canvas Carrying Bag:
This wearable helmet faithfully replicates the in-game model and comes complete with voice modulator speaker, functioning LED head lamp, and custom V.A.T.S. sound feature.

* Glow-in-the Dark World Terrain Map:
This physical, fully-colorized 21”x 21” glow in the dark vintage map showcases the six distinct regions of West Virginia complete with irradiated landmarks, towns, and wildlife.

* 24 Collectible Fallout Figurines:
Crafted from in-game 3D models, these detailed miniatures bring Fallout 76’s Vault Dwellers, Power Armored Soldiers, Creatures, and more to life.

* Tricentennial Steelbook: Exclusive to the Power Armor Edition, this decorated metal case is the ultimate collectible celebrating America’s 300 years of freedom.

* Fallout 76 Tricentennial Edition Bonus In-Game Items: Celebrate 300 years of freedom with the all-new Fallout 76 Tricentennial Edition, commemorating the opening of Vault 76. Be the talk of the town when you emerge from Vault 76 fully prepared and patriotically styled in the new American frontier!

* Access to the Fallout 76 B.E.T.A. (Break-It Early Test Application): Be one of the first to emerge into a new and untamed wasteland.

name: Rage 2: Collector's Edition
description:
The Rage 2 Collector’s Edition includes tons of great bonuses, including the mountable head of Ruckus the Crusher! This lovable half-dead mutant will live on your wall, talking and singing songs.

The limited Collector's Edition also includes:
* An exclusive steel book
* A Collector's Edition poster

Bonus Digital Content:
* Exclusive Bonus Mission -- Cult of the Death God.
* The Doom BFG.
* A Mutant Monster Truck Skin.
* Wasteland Wizard Cheat Codes.
* Progress Booster.
* Nicholas Raine Armor and Settler Pistol.
* An exclusive Battle Standard to fly from your vehicle.

name: Room54
description:
Room 54 is a first-person Horror/adventure Videogame for pc,mac and linux users. the game is currently under development by our small team passionate about games since younger age,we have years of exprerience in game development business but we decide to unify our passion and individual skill to create something more original,we care a lot about this project because his concept comes directly from the creative minds of our team. 
 
 
ARMED AND UNARMED: during the gameplay you will be armed and unarmed depends on what you can find in different locations. 
 
 
INTERACTIONS: Use objects to interacts, solve enigma and puzzles to unlock new areas 
 
 
CHALLENGING GAMEPLAY: Your enemy will not surrender easily, play with a competitive and smart AI with untipical and original weapons. 
 
CHARATERISTICS: 
 
explore terrifying building and places with an advanced graphics achivied with the powerfull of CryEngine 5. 
 
 
Follow the intriguing story discovering mysteries and using your intelligence examinating objects and ancient artifacts. 
 
 
use of high quality assets and soundbanks created with Wwise assure a total immersive gameplay.

name: Civilcontract
description: What Even Is CivilContract? CivilContract is a role-playing game (RPG) in CivilContract players will be able to do what ever they feel like their will be multiple jobs for each player to chose their path. Players can chose the road of the good life being a law enforcement officer to protect and serve were they will get their stranded issued general duties Holden commodore were they will be able to go out on patrol and keep the streets clean from drugs and crime. But you don't always have to take that road down the law enforcement area of life you can be a criminal with a whole open world to explore and to find ways to make money weather this means doing drugs or robbing stores or banks what ever it takes to earn that cold hard cash.

name: The Survivors
description: The Survivors is the Arctic-Western Battle Royale where 100 gold hunters fight for their claim in the Yukon Gold Rush. Storm eyes set the pace for the players, and bandits protect valuable loot. Players can use scrap to upgrade the 19th century weaponry. Join the fight and stake your claim!

name: Midnight Club: Los Angeles - South Central
The Fibos: Cosmic Invasion
description: The Fibos: Cosmic Invasion is a tower defense game set in the Fibos universe, your goal is to defend your boss and kill the enemy boss, you have 3 lanes to defend and attack trough ,take control of the mines to gain more crystals and upgrade your buildings to be more powerful ,your troops will get XP with every kill and be upgraded trough battle, you can always send wounded to medical center to heal, that way your upgraded recruits will be more effective.

name: Manny's Week
description: Manny's Week is a project taken on by a couple close friends using the engine Construct 2. It's intended to be a surreal experience through a particularly turbulent week of an increasingly unstable life.

name: Asteroid-Hunter
description:
Asteroid Hunter is a wave style Arcade game similar to Geometry Wars and Asteroids, I have taken the Legendary rocks of Asteroids, The game play of Geometry Wars combined-em into one than sprinkled on a coat of customization options.

Planned Asteroid-Hunter Features ATM.

The game is still under development but most these are already in the game.

name: Madden NFL 19: Hall of Fame Edition
Code Vein: Collector's Edition
description:
This edition includes the following
Game: Code Vein
Special Box
Mia Karnstein Figure (17cm tall)
Artbook (Code Vein World Report)
Original Soundtrack CD (22-track)
DLC

name: Red Dead Redemption 2: Collector's Box
description:
The Red Dead Redemption 2: Collector's Box features a curated assortment of outlaw essentials all packaged in a thick gauged metal tithing box.

Metal Tithing Box with Lock & Key: Inspired by the lockbox used by the Van der Linde gang to stash contributions to the camp's upkeep, this thick gauged metal box includes a lock & key, and features black metal band detailing and an engraved Cornwall Freight & Commodities plaque.

Collectable Challenge Coin: Featuring the majestic American Buffalo on one side and a scenic landscape on the other side, this engraved, gold-colored collectable coin comes in a magnetic presentation holder with a black, engraved plaque describing the history of this endangered species.

Double Sided Puzzle: This double-sided, 100-piece wooden jigsaw puzzle features an illustrated view of the bustling port of Saint Denis on one side, and a classically inspired Rockstar Games logo on the reverse.

Six Shooter Bandana: A staple for any frontier outlaw, this bandana features a traditional paisley-inspired pattern with hidden weapon iconography throughout.

Treasure Map: Printed on durable, unrippable paper, this exclusive treasure map reveals the location of some buried treasure that may start Arthur on a search for more riches hidden throughout the world of Red Dead Redemption 2.

Pin Set: This set of six individual pins includes representations of key weapons from Red Dead Redemption 2 including a shotgun, revolver and Dead Eye "X" marker. The set comes in a canvas carrying bag.

Playing Cards: Commemorate the outlaws of the Van der Linde gang with this fully illustrated deck of playing cards featuring key members of the gang including Arthur Morgan, John Marston, Javier Escuella, Bill Williamson and Dutch van der Linde.

Wheeler, Rawson and Co. Catalogue: The one-stop shop for everything from weapons to clothing, the Wheeler, Rawson and Co. Catalogue is an essential shopping tool for turn of the century life. This complete 150-page book is a replica of the edition found in stores throughout Red Dead Redemption 2.

12 Cigarette Cards: These beautifully-illustrated collectable cards can be found throughout the world of Red Dead Redemption 2. This physical collection includes one select card from each set like Famous Gunslingers and Outlaws, Stars of the Stage and Marvels of Travel and Locomotion.

name: Red Dead Redemption 2: Special Edition
description: America, 1899. The end of the wild west era has begun as lawmen hunt down the last remaining outlaw gangs. Those who will not surrender or succumb are killed.

name: Bucket Balls
description: Shoot those balls and fill up your buckets before the time runs out in this simple yet challenging puzzle game.

name: PeeTee Babybuu
description: Down the road, the neighbors knew...

name: Pool Elite
description: Chalk up your cue stick and get ready for Pool Elite, the most comprehensive, realistic and social billiards experience to date.

name: Day In Dementia
description: Day In Dementia is a short handdrawn story about Alzheimer, made by CrobbitArts.

name: Crazy Wheels
description: The floor is lava! Relive your childhood dream-races around the house with Crazy Wheels, a fast-paced, action-packed arcade racing game.

name: Myths of the World: Born of Clay and Fire
Abyss and Dark: The King's Secret Pledge
Ever After High Boots Trend Girl Games
Orphan Age
description: Orphan Age is a dystopian life sim game where you play not as the soldiers of war, but as the children left behind.

name: A Tale of Arms and Ale
Sea of Lies: Tide of Treachery
Mini Golf 2016 Pro: Real golf simulation 3D by Bulky Sports
Rhythmic Gymnastics Dream Team: Girls Dance
Fairy Mahjong Premium - The New 3D Majong
She Dreams Elsewhere
description: She Dreams Elsewhere is a surreal adventure RPG about dreams and the extent to which they mirror reality. You play as Thalia, an anxiety-ridden, comatose woman on a journey to defeat the nightmares preventing her from awakening, while also finding out how exactly this mess happened in the first place.

name: Trigon
description:
Trigon is a addicting brain teaser - a simple puzzle game that will challenge you, while also training your brain. Put your puzzle skills to the test with this exciting title. It will help you develop logic, and train your mental capacity.

The concept is simple - on a triangle board, combine puzzle blocks and clear the board by placing them strategically to create lines. Clear multiple lines at a time to get diamonds.

name: Transit City Touch
description: In Transit City Touch you get to build your own city, create your own transit network and start a thrilling card collection!

name: Space Roller Coaster VR
description: Jump into hyper speed and hold tight as you experience this galactic ride. Mars, Venus, Earth, the Stars and much more as you dive deeper into space. Remember the galaxy is vast and your journey starts here.

name: Bring Her Home
description: A survival walking sim, where HOW you survive is just as important as IF you survive.

name: Odd Island
description: Odd Island is a hold & gun, boss rush, time attack action-side-scrolling game. Odd Island describes the adventure of cute and small Chibi to win the Badge at the end of the beautiful island.

name: Transmogrify
description: An unusual 2D puzzle platformer that blends challenging action & handcrafted puzzles. Armed only with your peculiar gun (and a ton of power ups), you must transmogrify monsters into the tools you need to solve the puzzles. Escape the infested facility!

name: 1Dimensional Desperado
description: Grab your favourite brand of Snake Oil and sink some time into this Western-Themed, Card-Inspired, Procedurally-Generated, Straight-To-The-Point game!

name: Lets fall
description:
This easy-to-play and addictive arcade is going to give you a keen pleasure. You will hop from platform to platform with platform speed increased and width reduced as you progress through the game. There are achievements to give you permanent perks. Some of them will bring you additional points, while others will help to pass through the zones.

Please note that not every time you land on the middle of the platform you get the extra points, but every third (the bonus is accumulative and bring three points at once)

Features:
-Intuitive control
-Ease-to-play wherever you are
-Various achievements
-No in-game purchases.

Have fun!

name: Undead Valley
description: Undead Valley is a Zombie Survival RPG that puts the player into the role of a survivor during the Zombie Apocalypse. The player must survive by scavenging, fighting and building relationships with NPC's.

name: Kitty Run
description: An amusing and complicated runner about Kitty. You play as a cat who must save his kittens. Jump through the barriers and stay alive.

name: Bouldering Brawl
description: Play as one of many odd-unique characters (panda cosmonauts), dodge totally realistic mountaineering obstacles (swinging alphorns) and throw grotesque items (exploding goats) at your opponents in this ultimate friendship-destroying alpinism simulation

name: Rock Painting Story
description:
The game is pretty short to complete but have a lot of fun and a bit of drama. 
If support the developer, we will make a sequel of it!

name: Force Tanks
description:
In Force Tanks, you fight alone on a range against an army of opponents!
Help your army detain the enemy's offensive on his legendary tank!
You are fighting alone, in the name of an armistice all over the world!

name: Magnetic Pairs
description: A game made in combination of arcade and easy-logic gameplay styles. You need to magnetize and connect all orbs with a same color in tasks for logic and fast reaction.

name: Baikonur Space
description: Feel yourself as an astronaut. On your rocket, you can fly to distant space to meet new sensations. But for this you will need to improve your space vehicle and conduct a lot of training. So try to collect as much fuel as possible. With its help, drawings will be available to improve the missile. Thanks to them, your rocket will become the most powerful and fastest. Forward to the stars!:)

name: Up and Up
description: 3D parkour game that player need to find exit path before time.

name: U-Boot 1945
description: Commanding a submarine U-boot IIVc, get through the hostile dangerous waters full of traps, to the friendly shores.

name: Lucky Shot
description: Lucky Shot is a game in which a player can demonstrate his accuracy and knowledge of physics. The player uses a cannon from which to shoot and collect all the coins. But it's not so simple.

name: Lands of the Lost
description: A 3D Action RPG with Roguelike qualities, can you stop the Demon King??

name: HexTrains
description: Tower defense with trains! Destroy colored cargo containers that are transported by trains while building turrets that match the respective colors.

name: The Perfect Unit
description: The Perfect Unit is a puzzle. On each level you need to arrange items around the room in the correct order to bring the robot to the exit.

name: Feelin
description: Feelin is a creative world-building sandbox game. Build your imagination world with simple wood resources, for example, wood house, tower, sea port base, famous architectures. Also enjoy sharing your lovely scenes and artistic architectures on SNS.

name: The Duller
description: The Duller - is a dynamic retro-style game in which you have to defend the Earth..

name: Paper Valley
description: Paper Valley is a VR adventure game that challenges your ability to accurately throw paper planes. Skilfully glide and steer your planes toward targets across a beautiful fantasy land, and discover the mysteries of the sickness that has left it barren and desolate.

name: Kogent Defender
description: Kogent Defender enlists you to protect your home world from an encroaching enemy known as the Virtera. Under the command of the Kogent Mind you will take on this alien infestation and work to eliminate it completely.

name: Contact Draw: Football
description:
In Contact Draw: Football, you need to roll the ball into the goal using a pencil and improvised mechanisms that are on a level such as (trampoline, conveyor, platform) that can both interfere with you and help. 
At the choice of the player are presented 90 levels with different complexity and tests to compete in the game there is a timer and leaderboards of Steam.

name: Motorcycle, tricycle, ATV hill racing
description: Motorcycle, tricycle, ATV hill racing is en excellent opportunity for you to show your driving skills. Your task is to drive fast, but careful and overcome the different obstacles. Drive through the stone hills, ruined abandoned houses, go up and down on the stairs and much much more. With each level the game will become more and more difficult, so it will become more and more interesting.

name: Hellfire Fortress
description: In the Hellfire Fortress classic 1 vs 1 mode you’ll face sheer endless waves of demons and thus the goal is straight forward: Your Fortress needs to survive longer than your opponent’s! It’s your task to set up an army and strategically invest in economy while constantly leveling up your Fortress.

name: The RisenDead : VR
description:
Eliminate the zombies in the virtual reality of The Risen Dead VR and find out your viability. 
Other players can become your partner or a competitor. 
Experience thrilling thrill through attacking real-life zombies and other players.

name: Adore Picture Difference: Long Distance Love
Art Club Challenge
description: Solve challenges by making abstract art while unleashing your creativity. Playing as an art student striving to prove yourself, progress through the game’s narrative as you complete challenges. Push the boundaries of your artistic abilities, while tasked with creating familiar objects utilizing only a small color palate and limited shapes. Share your masterpieces with your friends through the online gallery and explore how others completed the same challenges while creating their own unique and personalized works of art.

name: Demon God's Tower
description:
The game starts off with the intro. You are a Death Knight who has fought in a few wars. You suddenly hear a voice that tells you about whats happening. The Demon God has awoken and you have to defeat him. You must travel the world and gather the other chosen ones, and make your way to his tower. 
There are a few playable characters as of now. There are secret characters.

name: Billionaire Dad Luxury Life Real Family Games
Bike Super Hero Stunt Driver Racing
NBA YoungBoy - Outside Today Piano Tiles
Mahjong Cards - Play classic mahjong solitaire with playing cards
Trucksform3d Offroad 3D Shooting Bigfoot Endless Racing Truck
Mother of All Battles
description:
Conquer the world starting from your single home city. Each city can build units (either tanks, planes, paratroopers, bombers, transports, destroyers, battleships, submarines or aircraft carriers) in order to explore the world and defeat the other five AI controlled enemy players.
There's a lot of AI in the computer's moves and the maps are randomly generated, so each game is interesting and challenging.

name: Galaxy Wars: Ice Empire
description:
Galaxy Wars: Ice Empire is an exciting mix of strategy and speed, storm the enemy planets and make your way in the galaxy.
Increase your fleet to every planet conquered and use the stored energy to improve the firepower, strength and speed of your ships.

name: Summer Beach Vacation Objects - Hidden Object Time
Dead Matter
description:
A rogue-lite that aims to quench the community’s thirst for a title that properly balances survival mechanics with fulfilling gameplay.

Dead Matter is a true sandbox survival horror. Players will fight to survive in a zombie-packed, post-apocalyptic world that fosters whichever play-style fits you best. Settle down and defend your home from outside threats with an expansive crafting and barricading system, cultivate and live off the land, or branch out, explore, and scavenge whatever vehicles, weapons, and food you may find in a zombie-plagued Alberta – alone, or with your friends.

name: The Bard's Tale IV: Barrows Deep - Ultimate Edition
The Bard's Tale IV: Barrows Deep - Platinum Edition
The Bard's Tale IV: Barrows Deep - Premium Edition
Epicedium
description:
Epicedium is a 4 vs 1 Asymmetric multiplayer survival horror title , play as a survivor and fight for you life to escape by co-operating with your teamates to Repair the radio and call for help or fight back to take the killer down,

Or play as a killer and hunt your prey with unique ability's.

name: Rockstar Alien Killers
description:
Take to the skies with the Rockstar Alien Killers in this aerial action game 
 
Grab your favourite plane, select your weapons of choice, turn the music to EXTREMELY LOUD and show off your flying skills in this action packed game. 
 
Join a band of washed-up rockstars who just happen to be able to fly planes and show the aliens who's best in aerial combat. 
Work your way through a variety of different "rock-tastic!" missions while earning mission bonuses and improving your Rockstar Rating. 
 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.addictive247.AlienKillers 
 
Official Trailer - https://youtu.be/VUODpQ_JpBM

name: ARia's Legacy
description: ARia’s Legacy is the first mobile escape room game using AR (augmented reality) technology. Instead of displaying objects on a table in front of you, it creates a virtual environment around your physical space that has you walking around your room discovering parts that were never there before. Through the power of AR, players can immerse themselves in 50 different levels of mystery anywhere using a mobile phone or tablet as they uncover the story behind ARia’s sudden disappearance and discover her legacy.

name: Upperz
description:
Upperz is a fast paced platform hell, featuring : 
 
- Fully Destructible environment and enemies 
 
- A bunch of anime style super abilities. Prepare to embrace chaos with Matter - 
 Bending ,to reach new heights with the Grappling hook, to summon Energy Blasts for some extra mayhem and many more... 
 
- Nimble controls and precise jump mechanism 
 
- Titans you can turn into smithereens (given that you find their week-points first!) 
 
- Hazards everywhere! Mainly neutral, some entities don't want you to die, they can be used in various ways but can break havoc if you do not thread carefully 
 
- Local Mutliplayer Co-op. The more the merrier, tag along with your friends to unleash the true destructive power of Upperz 
 
- Local Multiplayer Versus. Friendship destroyer up to 4 players 
 
- Arcade Mode. Climb a never-ending crumbling tower and stand proudly on top of the leaderboard

name: Beware
description: Beware is currently in early development. At the base, it's an open-world driving simulation where the player embarks on a long journey of information-gathering through exploration. One of the gameplay elements are intense, 70's movies style, car chases with challenging AI opponents. There are stealth element too where you can avoid being detected and explore the world undisturbed.

name: Night City Tokyo Drift: Clumsy Ninja Chasing Cars
Caveman HD
description: Caveman is a game inspired by the classic Lemmings developed by Psygnosis released for Amiga, DOS, et al in 1991.

name: Educational games for kids girls & boys apps free!
Resident Evil
description: Resident Evil was planned for a GameBoy Color adaptation in a project outsourced to British company HotGen Studios, Ltd. Intended for an Autumn 1999 release, it was repeatedly delayed due to programming issues, and ultimately cancelled in March 2000 in favour of M4, Ltd.'s alternate proposal for a new game made from the ground-up for the console, which became Resident Evil: Gaiden.

name: Imouto Ijime
description:
Short visual novel game (2-10 Hours). 
The game only has a single heroine. Your younger step sister. 
The games revolves around your interaction with her as your parents are newly married and has decided to live under the same roof.

name: Age of Solitaire : Build City
description:
Age of solitaire is a city building card game based on klondike solitaire rule.
A solitaire game that anyone can enjoy easily. It can be a bit challenging but fun!
Build your city while playing solitaire games!

name: Axe Champ
description:
Axe Champ is a axe throwing game !

Throw axes through the targets in Axe game !

Crush those targets and go all out for the best score!

name: Overpaint
description:
Overpaint is all about color in motion. The goal is simple: drag-and-drop the squares over the matching circles to clear them. To make new colors just overlap the 3 squares. Seems easy, right?
You have all the time yet each move counts…
Observe the colorful moving patterns and sharpen your skills. Join the color fun!

name: Four In A Row - Classic Games
Dream City Life: Urban Survival Edition
Survival: Man vs. Wild - Island Escape
description:
Wilderness survival challenge starts. What Bear Grylls did in "Man vs. Wild", you can do the same in this text-adventure game! 
 
This is an uninhabited wilderness. You lack of food and water, have to try your best to survive. Finally escape from the wild island and return to the civilized world. While you stay, you must learn the rules of survival, use your courage and wisdom to conquer the nature. 
 
To survive and escape, you have to craft camp, explore jungle, mountain, ruins, and so on territories, trade with natives, fight against beasts and cannibals, go deep into mystical relics, solve puzzles... 
 
As your exploration goes deeper, you get more and more weird feelings about this wilderness. Mystical ruins, legend heard from aborigines, occult mysteries, all these things make you believe it is not just a simple wilderness. This is not the last day for earth, but maybe the last day for you, be careful! 
 
Wilderness! Survival! Exploration! Mysteries! All in "Survival: Man VS. Nature".

name: Labyrinths of the World: Changing the Past HD
Shoot 2048 - reinvention of the classic puzzle
Grand Street Vegas Mafia Crime: Fight to Survive
My Pretend New York City - Big Apple Friends
London Craft: Crafting & Building Exploration Game
Ships Puzzles - Learning Toddler kids games 2 +
Zombies Everywhere! Augmented Reality Apocalypse (Halloween Edition)
Knife vs Fruit: Just Shoot It!
Five little monkeys jumping on the bed for toddler
My Kingdom for the Princess III HD
description: Finally! The great adventure continues! Familiar landscapes and great gameplay that combines features of time-management, simulation and strategy are waiting for you in the third part of My Kingdom for the Princess!

name: Fire in the hole
description: This is an online shooting game with Battle Royale mode. The game is played in a dark room, you can switch on the rifle flashlight for illuminating targeted areas, but always watch out for enemies who follow the light to sneak up on you!

name: Sega Pocket Club Manager
description:
The popular football RPG from SEGA, Pocket Club Manager, now available in English for the first time on mobile devices! Based on the popular “Let’s Make a Professional Soccer Club” series, Pocket Club Manager has been designed from the ground up to be as close to the original series as possible, complete with the same cycle of club management, player training, finance management and football simulation.
Join other players around the world and compete to create the greatest football club of all time!
Start off small and make it big! Become the Manager of a local football club, recruit real-life football stars, compete against the strongest teams, and take your shot at becoming the best in the world!
Gameplay is fast-paced and easy to pick up and play. Players will improve as your club gets bigger. Upgrade your clubhouse and stadium while conquering one league after another!

name: Dungeonhaven
description: A Knight restored to flesh from stone is guided by a sentient dungeon lusting after the power of creation. The Earth Core demands her knight drain other dungeon cores of their power, but can she control her pawn?

name: The Wizard of Oz Magic Match 3
Airport Simulator 2
description:
Experience exciting and varied tasks in the field of aircraft handling at a major international airport and take control of high-powered aircraft tractors, de-icing vehicles, and many more! Airport Simulator 2 features a total of five popular aircraft types and 14 different vehicles, offering a huge range of different tasks on the apron and taxiway.

These tasks need to be done, come rain or shine, day and night. Keep in mind that even the slightest delay in flight operations will cost you cold, hard cash.
Make sure that planes are refueled and boarded while also taking care of catering and baggage and cargo transport. Navigate airplanes to their parking positions with the aid of the follow-me car and get behind the wheel of the shuttle bus to transport passengers. Guide the ground power unit to the required position, prepare the passenger stair truck or jet bridge, and much more. When the weather starts to get cold, your skills in ice and snow removal will be put to the test.

name: Kim and Prostitute
description: Kim and Prostitute - in this game you will have to play for one of the last dictators of our time, but you will not fight against the whole world and not against individual countries, but only against the army of prostitutes. Game has 5000 achievements and comes with minimum allowable price.

name: World of Tea
description: World of Tea - a game where you have to take on the role of a teapot, and pour as much boiling water in the cups..

name: Defender Faith
description: Defender Faith is an atmospheric hardcore 2d platformer shooter. Pixel art is made in black white tones.

name: Dark Maze 2
description:
Get the feeling of enclosed space... 
Pass hundreds of kilometers to get out of hell... 
Be careful, because you don't know who is standing around the corner...

name: Teva 2

Come back to Teva 2 and ponostalgiruem. She will return you as a child when you were sitting in front of the TV for the console and having fun!
This 2D arknoid will make you ponastolgirovat about the past childhood and remember all those wonderful times.

name: Sliver-Sclicker

name: Krim: The Music Bot
description: KTMB is a hardcore 2D platformer with puzzle elements, where you take on the role of Krim - the Musical Bot.

name: Otto and the Ancient Worlds
description: Otto and the Ancient Worlds is an 8-bit 2D adventure platformer about an archaeologist who discovers an ancient library filled with magical books. Each book contains a living story of a mythology or folklore, and Otto mistakenly releases their contents into the world! Otto must return the mythology and folklore back to their books and destroy an 8-headed beast that has been released in the process.

name: Plutonium Pirates
description: In this action packed arcade adventure, pilot your trusted old chopper into enemy territory in search of nukes to abduct. Then blast your way out and mow down any enemy opposition you may encounter. You are, obviously, our last hope!

name: Mansion of Horrors
description: This is an adventure game laced with horror. To help the three trapped beauties get out, you have to rack your brain and solve all kinds of mysteries. When exploring the mansion, you may get scared by the “Trackers” who appear randomly. If you get caught, horrors await…

name: Five Rooms
description: Five Rooms is a unique puzzle game that tells the story of a lonely traveler stuck between worlds and time.

name: NekoBooM!
description:
This is an interesting story about a cat Girl-a warrior in the genre of Rhythm game with elements of a two-dimensional platformer.. 
Communication in the game takes place in the style of Japanese visual novel. 
If you're under 18, don't download because the game has R18 content with hentai scenes.

name: Order of the Assassin
description: Online free-for-all player vs. player game for windows 64 bit. Twelve stage single player campaign.

name: Cosplay Convention Crisis
description: For Jacob Kirby, today is the day of the big con. He's got his outfit ready. He hasn't forgotten his badge.The only thing that can derail an entire weekend of panels, cosplay, and consumerism is the fact that an inter-dimensional war might break out on the con floor!

name: Greed Adventure
description: Trademarked title in Japan by Bandai Namco.

name: The Internship
description: Young talented student Carli applies for a job as an assistant to a business lady Jan. They are not gay, but one night may change their lives... Try to find out what happened once in an office!

name: BulletRage
description:
BulletRage is a 1-4 player co-op adrenaline based arcade style twin stick shooter. Focusing on pure skill - You must survive twisted challenges, crush countless enemies, wield insanely devastating weapons, conquer brutal traps and storms of bullets.

Story: You are a contestant on an intergalactic game show. The prize? – The continued existence of our species! Conquered by an alien race – we must now survive this unnatural selection or face permanent extinction! Our final test is broadcast across the galaxy – Prove humanity’s worth using our greatest assets – BULLETS and RAGE!

name: Hunting on Myths
description: "Hunting on Myths" is an adventure MMORPG, which plays in the pirate age. Here the player can dive into the open world adventure as part of the Royal Navy, tradesmen or pirates and defend their land against other players or go on a treasure hunt.

name: Total Alarm
description: Total Alarm combines narrative adventure and resource management with a star-spanning science fiction setting and a retro-future style. A once celebrated top-class engineer, you've been sentenced to menial work on the fringes of settled space. Your crime? Wrongthink, just one of the many violations that can prompt the Collective's harsh reprisals. In fact, you'll want to avoid the least slip in your efforts to keep the lights on and air flowing through the deep-space derelicts you've been tasked with maintaining. Only vigilance will keep you from the ultimate punishment: a short walk out of an open airlock.

name: Maybe Drinking. Russian Style
description: In this game you'll have to help your hero with getting completely drunk in the various places of such a grand country like Russia. But don't think that everything gonna be easy - you'll face lots of different obstacles which you'll have to avoid to find the True Harmony.
